int minSubArrayLen(int target, int* nums, int numsSize) {
    int length = 100001;
    int start = 0;
    int sum = 0;
    for(int end = 0; end < numsSize; end++) {
        sum += nums[end];
        while (sum >= target) { //è¿™ä¸ªwhileæ˜¯ç²¾é«“ï¼ï¼ï¼ æ»‘åŠ¨åˆå§‹çª—å£
            if ((end - start + 1) < length) {
                length = end - start + 1;
            }            
            sum -= nums[start];
            start++;
        }
    }
    if (length < 100001) {
        return length;
    }
    else {
        return 0;
    }
}
```



### [59. èºæ—‹çŸ©é˜µ II](https://leetcode.cn/problems/spiral-matrix-ii/)

